no2}}Loss\n|2-2\n|align=left|Cash Edwards\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|10-15\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=5|March 17, 2000\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=5|[[NCAA Division I Wrestling Championships|2000 NCAA Division I Wrestling Championships]]\n|-\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|2-1\n|align=left|Doug Lee\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|4-6\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2-0\n|align=left|Zach Breitenbach\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|16-9\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1-0\n|align=left|Jeff Knupp\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|Forfeit\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n==Pay-per-view bouts==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!No.\n!Event\n!Fight\n!Date\n!Venue\n!City\n!PPV Buys\n|-\n|1.\n|[[UFC 182]]\n|'''Jones''' vs. '''Cormier'''\n|January 3, 2015\n|[[MGM Grand Garden Arena]]\n|[[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas, Nevada]], U.S.\n|800,000\n|-\n|2.\n|[[UFC 187]]\n|'''Johnson''' vs. '''Cormier'''\n|May 23, 2015\n|[[MGM Grand Garden Arena]]\n|[[Las Vegas Valley|Las Vegas, Nevada]], U.S.\n|375,000\n|-\n|3.\n|[[UFC 192]]\n|'''Cormier''' vs. '''Gustafsson'''\n|October 3, 2015\n|[[Toyota Center]]\n|[[Houston, Texas]], U.S.\n|250,000\n|-\n|4.\n|[[UFC 210]]\n|'''Cormier''' vs. '''Johnson 2'''\n|April 8, 2017\n|[[KeyBank Center]]\n|[[Buffalo, New York|Buffalo]], [[New York (state)|New York]], U.S\n|300,000\n|-\n|5.\n|[[UFC 214]]\n|'''Cormier''' vs. '''Jones 2'''\n|July 29, 2017\n|[[Honda Center]]\n|[[Anaheim, California|Anaheim]], [[California]], U.S.\n|860,000\n|-\n|6.\n|[[UFC 226]]\n|'''Miocic''' vs. '''Cormier'''\n|July 7, 2018\n|[[T-Mobile Arena]]\n|[[Las Vegas Strip|Paradise, Nevada]], U.S.\n|400,000\n|-\n|7.\n|[[UFC 230]]\n|'''Cormier''' vs. '''Lewis'''\n|November 3, 2018\n|[[Madison Square Garden]]\n|[[New York City]], [[New York (state)|New York]], U.S.\n|250,000\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" |Total sales\n!3,585,000\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of current UFC fighters]]\n* [[List of Strikeforce alumni]]\n* [[List of male mixed martial artists]]\n* [[List of UFC champions]]\n* [[List of UFC bonus award recipients]]\n* [[Ultimate Fighting Champions